<div class='user-info'>
<a class='avatar' href='http://www.splicetoday.com/profile/eureka'>
<img alt="Exclamation_mark_small" class="avatar" src="/vault/avatars/0000/1293/Exclamation_mark_small.png?1290922010" />
</a>
<div class='screenname'>
<a href="http://www.splicetoday.com/profile/eureka">eureka</a>
